{Porirua is a city in the Wellington Region of New Zealand, immediately north of the city of Wellington, with their central business districts 20 km apart. A large proportion of the population commutes to Wellington, so it may be considered a satellite city. Porirua can be located in the HealthMap interactive map at: http://healthmap.org/r/1KlG. - Mod.CP]
